ProtocolSearch - Class in com.lukeleber.scandroid.gui
As mandated by SAE J1978 §7.1, this class provides the following functionality: Provides an "Automatic hands-off determination of the communication protocol" Informs the user that bus initialization is occurring Prevent user intervention while each individual protocol test is occurring Upon failure, advise the user of the following: That communication with the vehicle could not be established To confirm that the ignition key is in the "ON" position To check the emissions label or vehicle service information to confirm that the vehicle is OBD equipped and compliant To confirm that the external test equipment is connected to the vehicle correctly Notifies the user of the number of failed initialization attempts Retries the initialization process until succeeding or the user cancels TODO: This class has two issues: a GUI listview problem and what I feel is an ICE.
